00:01:24.350 --> 00:01:27.850
A look at Stackoverflow
reveals over 53,000 Git

00:01:27.850 --> 00:01:28.780
related questions.

00:01:28.780 --> 00:01:30.332
But help is on the way.

00:01:30.332 --> 00:01:31.790
First Aid Git is
a searchable index

00:01:31.790 --> 00:01:33.705
of the most commonly
asked Git questions.

00:01:33.705 --> 00:01:35.580
Curious how to undo a
change that you've just

00:01:35.580 --> 00:01:36.440
pushed to Master?

00:01:36.440 --> 00:01:39.137
You can find that answer and
more, or submit a pull request

00:01:39.137 --> 00:01:39.970
to add to the index.

